{
  "stem": "1641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They just flew on up from the floor to the truck, tossed in, bang down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "High-temperature cases and lost legs and arms or whatever, who couldn't walk up on the truck, was thrown up and thrown in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after about two hours, the trucks came back with the shoes and the uniforms to be washed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were already gassed, finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think some factor could have been that I had very blonde hair in those days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I'm darker, but I was very light blonde with blue eyes and very white skin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the SS man could have thought that maybe I'm just a-- a German criminal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, he didn't analyze me-- who am I?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could-- there were Germans amongst us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "German-- there were Germans who were homosexual, Germans who were priests, Germans who were socialists or communists.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were Germans who were just-- who had just murdered their father or-- or hold up a bank or criminals, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he could have thought, if for one second, that, oh, he's OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, he's blonde and, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was-- if anybody who had black hair or dark skin-- that-- that was a Jew, for sure.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anybody blonde, that could-- could have been a Christian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that's how I survived it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was absolute miracle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the second miracle came couple of days after, when the commandant of the-- of the building, a-- a German Christian-- he was a former socialist leader or something.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was about 55 year old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a real socialist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, look, Frank, I won't let you go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
